# Remote ads (ski_jahorina)

## How it works
1. App fetches `GET /v1/ads-config/ski_jahorina` (~every 3 days) -> `AdsPolicyStore`
2. Hub navigation increments `AdClickStore` and calls `shouldShowAd(screenId, clicks)`
3. If enabled and `clicks % everyN == 0`, show interstitial then navigate

## Wired screen_ids
`weather`, `lifts`, `cameras`, `map`, `useful_info`, `apartments`

## Ops (no app release needed)
- Toggle/frequency: UPDATE `ad_screen_policies` for existing wired `screen_id`
- Cache TTL ~3 days (`AdsConfigFetcher.CACHE_TTL_MS`)

## App release needed
- Adding a **new** `screen_id` requires: constant in `AdsScreens`, default in `AdsPolicyStore`, and a call site that checks it

## Do not
- Expect a DB-only row to monetize a screen with no `shouldShowAd` check
- Change backend schema for simple enable/frequency edits
